The Council long service awards are paid as a set value and are paid irrespective of pay level and gender. 
 

Pay by Quartiles 

 
Quartile data breaks down statistics for four equal proportions of employees, from the lowest earning 25% 
of staffs (lower quartile) to the highest earning 25% of staffs (upper quartile).    
 

 

