 Employees included in the Gender Pay Gap data 
 
Included in the data are the Council’s employees (who are paid via the payroll). The figures do not include 
self-employed workers. The information for this group of individuals is being reviewed to enable their data 
to be included in future publications. 
 
The figures set out above have been calculated using the standard methodologies used in the Equality Act 
2010 (Gender Pay Gap Information) Regulations 2017. 
 
