Exclusion of Living Wage & Apprentices – for comparative purposes 

 

20% of the workforce was within the Council pay bandings of Kirklees Living Wage and Apprentices, the 
roles in this banding of employees is predominately cleaning services to schools. The following data 
excludes these employees from the gender pay gap calculation. 
 
There were 6197 employees in position, 4174 females and 2023 males. 
 

  

 69% Of the Council workforce are women 

